Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流 严禁用于商业途径
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译: Grim ch1plus1\N校对: Grim
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,时间轴调整: 程风吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我总相信 是那些你没法选择的事物\N{\rEN}I always believed it was the things you don't choose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,造就了你\N{\rEN}that makes you who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家乡\N{\rEN}Your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你的邻里\N{\rEN}Your neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的亲人\N{\rEN}Your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的人总是为这些事物骄傲\N{\rEN}People here take pride in these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好像那是他们的成就\N{\rEN}Like it was something they'd accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的灵魂包裹在皮囊里\N{\rEN}The bodies around their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后又被城市笼罩\N{\rEN}The cities wrapped around those.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,片名: 《失踪的宝贝》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子一直住在这个街区\N{\rEN}I lived on this block my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人多数也一样\N{\rEN}Most of these people have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我的工作是寻找失踪者\N{\rEN}When your job is to find people who are missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,知道他们的老家在哪里总是有帮助的\N{\rEN}it helps to know where they started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我找的是那些\N{\rEN}I find the people who started in the cracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,钻进地缝里不见的人\N{\rEN}and then fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市或许很残酷\N{\rEN}This city can be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候我问牧师 怎样才能既保证自己上天堂\N{\rEN}When I was young, I asked my priest how you could get to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又不被世上的各种邪恶力量吞噬\N{\rEN}and still protect yourself from all the evil in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我 上帝是这么对自己的孩子说的\N{\rEN}He told me what God said to his children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"你们是狼群中的羔羊"\N{\rEN}"You are sheep among wolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"既要像毒蛇一样精明"\N{\rEN}"be wise as serpents,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"也要像鸽子一样清白"\N{\rEN}"yet innocent as doves."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 你就住在马路对面 是吗?\N{\rEN}You live just across the street. Is that right, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拐角上那座就是我的房子\N{\rEN}That one on the corner, that's our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 让安妮特上高中 要…\N{\rEN}You know, to get Annette in high school, you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我听说他们办了开幕式 - 对 我也听说了\N{\rEN}- I heard they had an opening. - Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是 她脸上总是挂着微笑\N{\rEN}The thing is, she always had a smile on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是这样 一直在笑\N{\rEN}That was her. She was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会拐走我的小姑娘?\N{\rEN}I mean, who would take my little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她从没伤害过任何人 从没…\N{\rEN}She never hurt anybody, never caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是谁 如果她在你手上\N{\rEN}Whoever you are, if you have her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,马上放了她\N{\rEN}you just let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会起诉你\N{\rEN}Now, we won't charge you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你听到我说话 快让她回家\N{\rEN}but if you're out there, just let her come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗?让她回家\N{\rEN}All right? Let her come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会拐走我的小姑娘?\N{\rEN}I mean, who would take my little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他妈的警察 - 她从没闯过祸\N{\rEN}- You fucking cops. - She never caused no trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她从没打过架 她是个小乖乖\N{\rEN}she never got in any fights, she's a sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这也太夸张了 - 她是个好孩子\N{\rEN}- This is just unbelievable. - She was a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,警察全体出动 站在那房子外面\N{\rEN}The whole force standing outside the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,背着手 守在人行道上\N{\rEN}guarding the sidewalk with their arms crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 难道绑匪又回来了?\N{\rEN}I mean, are the kidnappers coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达·麦克雷蒂被人从家中绑走\N{\rEN}Amanda McCready was taken from her home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,时间是星期三晚上8:00到8:30之间\N{\rEN}between 8:00 and 8:30 Wednesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她今年四岁 金发 绿眼…\N{\rEN}She's four years old, has blond hair and green eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,…体重35磅 身高40英寸\N{\rEN}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...weighs 35 pounds and is 40 inches tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道我爱你 对吗? - 对 我知道\N{\rEN}- You know I love you, right? - Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,饱受指责的警察和疲惫不堪的市民\N{\rEN}A beleaguered police force and a weary citizenry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只能指望少得可怜的一点线索\N{\rEN}have been left with so little to cling to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一条毯子 一个后门 和一个名叫米拉贝尔的布娃娃\N{\rEN}A blanket, a back door, and a doll named Mirabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,街坊邻居都集合起来了\N{\rEN}The neighborhood's really coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要开个会\N{\rEN}We're gonna have a rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都要警戒 今晚我们要守夜\N{\rEN}Everyone's gonna have a vigil. We're gonna have a vigil tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居们都提高了警惕\N{\rEN}You know, the neighborhood's all alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都在注意有什么风吹草动…\N{\rEN}everybody's alert of what's going on and everything that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在周围发了传单 贴了寻人启事 我们全都做了\N{\rEN}The surroundings. We got flyers up, posters up, we have all that stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让大家都知道这事 让大家都来找阿曼达\N{\rEN}So everybody's well aware and everybody's looking for Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在相关新闻里 负责预防针对儿童犯罪的\N{\rEN}In related news, the Boston police captain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,波士顿警监\N{\rEN}responsible for preventing crimes against children
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚说了一些\N{\rEN}spoke a few words a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,安慰的话语\N{\rEN}words of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解失去女儿的痛苦 我们不会辜负大家\N{\rEN}I know the pain of losing a daughter. We will not fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将追查每一条线索\N{\rEN}We will pursue every avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解那个妈妈吗?\N{\rEN}Do you know the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·道伊尔警监详细介绍失踪的 多尔切斯特女孩…\N{\rEN}Captain Jack Doyle on details of the missing Dorchester girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微知道一点 那时我是新生 她是高年级的\N{\rEN}Little bit. I was a freshman, she was a senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她在柱子下面给麦克·古雷口交\N{\rEN}She was blowing Mike Gulley down the post
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他还是14岁的纯真少男 在佛蒙特州给奶牛挤奶\N{\rEN}when he was still 14 and innocent and milking cows up Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道什么叫纯真\N{\rEN}I don't know about innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,据母亲说 阿曼达可能带着自己的一个娃娃\N{\rEN}Her mother says Amanda may be carrying a little girl of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,人们最后一次看到阿曼达时 她和她最喜欢的娃娃米拉贝尔在一起\N{\rEN}Mirabelle was last seen with Amanda. It's her favorite doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这太可怕了\N{\rEN}This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你是电视台 就不会这么想了 - 关了它\N{\rEN}- Not if you're Channel 9. - Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEN}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂 安姬 去开门吧? - 我在浴室里\N{\rEN}- Hey, Angie. Get the door? - I'm in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的才7:00!大清早的!\N{\rEN}It's 7:00! Seven in the fucking morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么?\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是帕特里克·肯奇吗?\N{\rEN}Are you Patrick Kenzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是 - 碧·麦克雷蒂和莱昂内尔·麦克雷蒂\N{\rEN}- Yeah. - Bea and Lionel McCready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的外甥女三天前被绑架了\N{\rEN}Our niece was kidnapped three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,请进 请进 真对不起\N{\rEN}Please, come on in. Come on in. I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居家的孩子爱捣蛋\N{\rEN}You know, there's been some problems with kids in the neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们老是按了门铃就跑\N{\rEN}kind of ding-dong ditch, ringing the buzzer and running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我刚才会爆粗口\N{\rEN}So that's the reason for the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 - 我们可以晚点再来\N{\rEN}- Oh. - Well, we can come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 不用 别客气\N{\rEN}No. Please, please. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们就是… 对不起 这里太乱了\N{\rEN}Here, we're just... I'm sorry about the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在… 我最近有个案子 还有很多其他案子\N{\rEN}We've been... I had a late case, and a lot of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在… 一直在工作\N{\rEN}We've just been... We've just been working a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚还在弄一个案子 所以我们…\N{\rEN}we worked on a case last night, you know, so we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 请坐吧\N{\rEN}Please sit down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,或者…\N{\rEN}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的合伙人马上就过来 她在别的房间里\N{\rEN}My associate'll be in in just a minute. She's in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么要我们帮忙的?\N{\rEN}How can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道在街坊邻居里\N{\rEN}Do you know people in the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人不肯和警察说话吧?\N{\rEN}who don't talk to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对 有一两个\N{\rEN}Yeah, one or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想雇你们来加强对阿曼达的调查\N{\rEN}We wanna hire you to augment the investigation of Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\rEN}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道在拉姆西案*里 那家人雇了 私家侦探吧? （*1996年轰动全美的儿童选美皇后被害案 案犯在2006年才落网）\N{\rEN}You know how in JonBenet Ramsey the family hired investigators?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么… 你们雇外人帮忙 警察没意见吗?\N{\rEN}So... Are the police all right with youse hiring outside help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,警察应该关心的是怎么找到我的外甥女\N{\rEN}The police need to worry about finding my niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是安姬·杰纳罗 是帕特里克的同事\N{\rEN}Hi. I'm Angie Gennaro. I work with Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是碧·麦克雷蒂 这是我丈夫莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}Hello. I'm Bea McCready. This is my husband, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 他们想雇我们\N{\rEN}- How do you do? - They wanna hire us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来加强调查\N{\rEN}to augment the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们该去找精密侦探事务所\N{\rEN}You should talk to Precision Investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁?我… - 我不知道 我的意思是…\N{\rEN}- Who? I... - I don't know, I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听他们说吧 安姬\N{\rEN}Well, let's hear them out, Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不是专找失踪者的侦探吗?\N{\rEN}Well, aren't you missing persons detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你们在报上登的广告就是这么写的\N{\rEN}Yeah, that's what your ad says in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们是专找失踪者的侦探\N{\rEN}Yeah, we are. We are missing persons detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 她… 我想安姬的意思是说\N{\rEN}I'm sorry, she... I think that what Angie means to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么回事 应该向你们说明\N{\rEN}just for the sake of disclosure, up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的经验主要在于 寻找那些失踪者\N{\rEN}our experience has been primarily, you know, finding missing persons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙失踪是因为…\N{\rEN}who've gone missing that they...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不肯再交动力雪橇的分期付款\N{\rEN}You know, they just stop payments on their Jet Ski
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,搬到新罕布什尔州去了…\N{\rEN}and they went to New Hampshire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在本州的每个警察都在找你们的外甥女\N{\rEN}Every police officer in this state is looking for your niece right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢说我们能帮多少忙\N{\rEN}And I'm not sure how much more help we could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来帮忙也没有坏处 对吗?\N{\rEN}Well, you're not gonna do any harm, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 听我说 我有爱迪生公司给我的养老金\N{\rEN}All right, look. I got a pension coming up with Edison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以用它作抵押 如果… - 不 不是这个意思\N{\rEN}- So, that's collateral, if... - No. It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么难办? 警察不希望我来这\N{\rEN}Why is this so hard? The cops don't want me coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱昂内尔不希望我来这 - 别担心\N{\rEN}- Lionel don't want me coming here. - Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在你们还不想接这份工作? - 不 我们不是不想接这份工作…\N{\rEN}- Now you don't want the job? - No, it's not that we don't want the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们作这样的决定之前 都要先私下商量商量\N{\rEN}We consult privately before we make decisions like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 那天海琳送她上了床\N{\rEN}- We do. - Helene puts her to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去道蒂家看电视 大概看了半个钟头\N{\rEN}She goes across to Dottie's. Maybe gone a half hour, watches TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等她回到家里 阿曼达就不见了\N{\rEN}Then she comes home and Amanda is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她看的是《换妻》\N{\rEN}She was watching Wife Swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她记得很清楚 因为这是她最喜欢的节目\N{\rEN}She remembers, 'cause that's her favorite show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩住在楼上?\N{\rEN}And do youse two live upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们父母去世时给我们 留了一个单元 给我妹妹也留了一个\N{\rEN}Yeah, when our folks died they left us a unit and my sister a unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你知道 我们基本上别无选择\N{\rEN}so, you know, basically we got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,房子里的那些声音\N{\rEN}And with the acoustics in the apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你躲不过的\N{\rEN}you can't get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么不过去看看呢?\N{\rEN}Why don't you just come over the house, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 和海琳谈谈吧 - 莱昂内尔 和海琳谈?\N{\rEN}- Just talk to Helene, you know. - Lionel, talk to Helene?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是没有表现出来 其实她现在很痛苦\N{\rEN}Look, she don't show it, but she's hurting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 拜托! - 好了 听我说 好吗?\N{\rEN}- Please. Please! - All right. Lookit, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是圣人 明白吗? 我也有过自己的问题\N{\rEN}I was no saint. All right? I had my own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在22岁时曾经自暴自弃 是碧让我浪子回头的\N{\rEN}I took a hard bust at 22. Bea straightened me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹海琳还没这样的经历\N{\rEN}My sister Helene has not had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和母亲谈谈是我们起码该做的\N{\rEN}Talking to the mother's the least we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会过去的 - 太谢谢了\N{\rEN}- We'll come right over. - Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}Yeah. Pleasure, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就住在公园边上那座褐色的 三层公寓楼里\N{\rEN}Oh, you'll find us in that brown three-decker by the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们知道地址 - 如今那地方你很难迷路了\N{\rEN}- You know where it is. - Be hard to miss today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧 天哪\N{\rEN}Look at this. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全街区的人都聚在这儿了\N{\rEN}Fucking block party here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去年这里有四个佛得角移民被杀\N{\rEN}Four Cape Verdeans got killed here last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没人关心\N{\rEN}No one gave a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的生活很美好 对吧?\N{\rEN}We have a good life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题里有陷阱吧?\N{\rEN}Is that a trick question?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望在垃圾箱里找到他们的小孩\N{\rEN}I don't wanna find their little kid in a dumpster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她不在垃圾箱里 宝贝\N{\rEN}Maybe she's not in a dumpster, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望小孩被虐待三天后才被人找到\N{\rEN}I don't wanna find a little kid after they've been abused for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 没人愿意这样\N{\rEN}Hon, nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 我们这就上去和他们谈\N{\rEN}Listen, we'll just go up and we'll talk to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是谈过以后你不想接手 我不会和你争的\N{\rEN}and you don't wanna do it after that, I won't argue with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 请进\N{\rEN}Hi. Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳\N{\rEN}Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是帕特里克·肯奇 安吉拉·杰纳罗\N{\rEN}This is Patrick Kenzie, Angela Gennaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 我记得在高中里见过你\N{\rEN}- Hi. - I remember you from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你还是有点臭架子 嗯?\N{\rEN}I see you're still a little conceited, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,道蒂 劳驾 回避一下好么?\N{\rEN}Would you excuse us, Dottie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,道蒂是我最好的朋友 莱昂内尔 只要她乐意 就可以呆在我家\N{\rEN}Dottie's my best friend, Lionel. She could be in my house if she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳 我们不想惹你生气\N{\rEN}Helene, we don't wanna get in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只想问几个关于你女儿的问题\N{\rEN}We're just gonna ask you a couple questions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,问完了我们就走\N{\rEN}about your daughter, then we'll be out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在人人都想掺一脚了 - 我知道\N{\rEN}- Everyone wants their part now. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经跟警察说了四十遍\N{\rEN}I already talked to the cops forty times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 我们又要耽误你的时间 - 我们不是警察\N{\rEN}- We're sorry to take up your time. - Listen, we're not the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是碧特丽斯请我们来的\N{\rEN}Beatrice asked us to come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看看是不是能帮忙找你女儿\N{\rEN}and see if we could help out finding your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,碧来管什么闲事? 那是我的孩子\N{\rEN}Why don't Bea mind her business? It's my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为现在人人都想来出风头\N{\rEN}'Cause everyone gotta have their moment, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对吗? - 对\N{\rEN}- Right? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,碧特丽斯自己掏钱请这些人 帮忙找阿曼达\N{\rEN}Beatrice hired these people to help find Amanda with her own money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说你最好懂点礼貌\N{\rEN}so you had better show them the goddamn courtesy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对他们放尊重点! - 她现在正伤心呢 混蛋\N{\rEN}- and respect they deserve! - She's in grieving, prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她想怎么伤心是她的事 道蒂\N{\rEN}She could grieve how she wants, Dottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你又不是这家的人! - 混蛋\N{\rEN}- You don't live here! - Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的别冲她嚷嚷 莱昂内尔 你又不是她爸爸!\N{\rEN}Don't you fucking yell at her, Lionel. You ain't her father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,滚你的 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}Fuck you, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,回家自慰去吧 操你\N{\rEN}Go fuck yourself. Cocksucker. Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我滚蛋\N{\rEN}Get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEN}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 - 也许我们该走了\N{\rEN}- I'm sorry. - Maybe we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能理解 对不起 - 没什么\N{\rEN}- I understand. I'm sorry. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该走了?\N{\rEN}Maybe we should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在走廊里说会儿话 好吗?\N{\rEN}Look. Can we all just have a few words in the hallway, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪了 海琳\N{\rEN}Excuse us, Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 海琳的情绪有点问题 - 不是这样的 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}- Helene's got emotional problems. - It's not that, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是怎样? - 她是个贱货!\N{\rEN}- What is it, then? - She's a cunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 碧特丽斯 别说这种话 - 上帝作证 这是实话\N{\rEN}- Beatrice, don't use that word. - God help me, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个孩子 我不知道她在哪儿\N{\rEN}This is a child. And I don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,唔…\N{\rEN}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来帮忙也没坏处 对吧?\N{\rEN}We can't do any harm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 碧 好了\N{\rEN}It's all right, Bea. It's all right, Bea. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\rEN}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她很文静 一直在努力做个好孩子\N{\rEN}Well, she's quiet. She tries very hard to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,说说海琳吧?她的朋友怎样? 和她来往的人呢?\N{\rEN}What about Helene? Her friends? People she hangs out with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多人来她家作客吗?\N{\rEN}She got a lot of people come by the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 她总是泡在菲尔莫\N{\rEN}I don't know. She's at the Fillmore all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在菲尔莫酒馆?\N{\rEN}She's at the Fillmore Lounge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对 她天天喝酒\N{\rEN}Yeah, she drinks every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她这是遗传的 胎里毛病 我们的父母也是这样\N{\rEN}She's got the gene, you know? The disease. Our parents had it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她嗑药吗?\N{\rEN}She use drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她会吸一点可卡因\N{\rEN}I think she does a little coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一点是多少?\N{\rEN}How much is a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 大概一星期有几次吧 怎样才算是很多?\N{\rEN}I don't know. Few times a week, maybe. I mean, how much is a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一星期几次已经很多了\N{\rEN}Few times a week's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那么她吸得很多 这种事我不清楚的\N{\rEN}Then she does a lot. I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自己戒掉的 已经23年没碰过了 所以我身体很好\N{\rEN}I put the plug in the jug myself, I got 23 years sobriety, so, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺你\N{\rEN}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看她的房间你们不介意吧?\N{\rEN}Do you mind if we see her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 连家具也绑走了? - 帕特里克\N{\rEN}- Kidnapped the furniture, too? - Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,下班人员调查\N{\rEN}10-7 investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还没解决?\N{\rEN}Solved it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,警监 我是帕特里克·肯奇 这是我的合伙人安姬·杰纳罗\N{\rEN}Captain, Patrick Kenzie. This is my associate, Angie Gennaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼?\N{\rEN}Mmm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见碧特丽斯出去雇了些人\N{\rEN}I see Beatrice went on and hired someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这应该不是你的建议\N{\rEN}I take it that wasn't your recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEN}It was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人为了雇每一个肯收信用卡的 家伙 会把房子全抵押出去\N{\rEN}That woman would mortgage her home to every snake doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要她觉得他们能帮忙找她外甥女\N{\rEN}taking credit cards if she thought it would help find her niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作已经够难了 还要应付这些耍把戏的\N{\rEN}My job's hard enough without inviting the circus in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,警监 我们做这事不是为了钱\N{\rEN}Captain, this isn't about the money for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们以前调查过诱拐案吗?\N{\rEN}You ever investigated an abduction before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想麦克雷蒂太太是希望我们\N{\rEN}I think Mrs. McCready was hoping we could help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看在街坊邻居的份上出一把力 警民协作嘛\N{\rEN}with the neighborhood aspect of this investigation, the people, you know.
