Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.80,0:43:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 我不会拿这事来责怪你\N{\rEN}No, no. I won't hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.60,0:43:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我要拿什么事来责怪你吗?\N{\rEN}You know what I'll hold against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.11,0:43:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有过一次做成交易的机会 你说你认识他\N{\rEN}We had one chance to make this deal. You said you knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.68,0:43:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你能办到 但是你办砸了\N{\rEN}You said you could do it and you fucked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.35,0:43:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只好去申请窃听许可 开始侦查\N{\rEN}Now I gotta get a warrant for a tap, start surveillance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.78,0:43:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,希望老天让我们走运\N{\rEN}hope to Christ we get lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.72,0:43:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 要是阿曼达因此丧了命\N{\rEN}You know, if Amanda dies because of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.89,0:43:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不用拿这事来责怪你\N{\rEN}I won't have to hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.06,0:43:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己也会内疚很久的\N{\rEN}You'll hold it against yourself for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.02,0:44:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿我们没把这事搞砸\N{\rEN}Hope we didn't fuck this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.70,0:44:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂 - 奶酪来了电话\N{\rEN}- Yeah. - Cheese called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.04,0:44:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说他愿意拿阿曼达作交易 不过要在今晚\N{\rEN}Says he'll take the deal with Amanda, but he wants to go tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.94,0:44:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 太好了 - 也好也不好\N{\rEN}- Great. - Well, it is and it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.64,0:44:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如今警局的电话都有录音\N{\rEN}They record calls at the station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.41,0:44:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克拿到了记录 - 什么意思?\N{\rEN}- Jack got a hold of the transcript. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.05,0:44:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是说 我们的警徽现在差不多 要被没收了\N{\rEN}It means our badges are basically fucking forfeit at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.18,0:44:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他要你们俩马上过来\N{\rEN}He wants you both down here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.12,0:44:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 还有 奶酪说他在邮箱里 留了点东西\N{\rEN}Oh, and, hey, Cheese said he left something in a mailbox
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.32,0:44:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以证明阿曼达在他手上\N{\rEN}to prove that he's got Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.32,0:45:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,身为警察的被害儿童父亲发誓 不让悲剧重演
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.14,0:45:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是今天早上一段电话录音的抄本\N{\rEN}This is a transcript of a recorded call that came in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.45,0:45:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,读读重点标出的那段好吗?\N{\rEN}Care to read the highlighted portion?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.72,0:45:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大声点\N{\rEN}Aloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.13,0:45:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\N{\rEN}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.59,0:45:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来电者: 妈的 你们最好有我的钱\N{\rEN}"Caller: Bitch, you better have my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.97,0:45:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,布里桑特侦探: 你是谁?\N{\rEN}"Detective Bressant: Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.17,0:45:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来电者: 你知道我是谁 笨蛋…\N{\rEN}"The caller: You know who the fuck this is, fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.81,0:45:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,海地语粗话 如果你们想要回那女孩\N{\rEN}"Creole curse words. If you want that girl back,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.38,0:45:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚就来昆西找我\N{\rEN}"you need to meet me up Quincy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.91,0:45:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只要迟了一分钟 我就把那女孩扔进湖里\N{\rEN}"Fuck around for a minute and I'll throw that girl in the lake."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.52,0:46:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的湖是指废采石场里的水潭\N{\rEN}The lake he refers to is the water in the abandoned quarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.45,0:46:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,布里桑特侦探未经授权\N{\rEN}Detective Bressant goes on to make an unauthorized ransom arrangement
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.92,0:46:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就打算在那个地方用13万美元\N{\rEN}to exchange Amanda McCready for $ 130,000 tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.73,0:46:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,赎回阿曼达·麦克雷蒂\N{\rEN}in just that location.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.77,0:46:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,经过一番讨论以后 布里桑特侦探好心地交出了\N{\rEN}After some discussion, Detective Bressant was kind enough
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.44,0:46:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西\N{\rEN}to produce this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.20,0:46:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,认识吗?\N{\rEN}Recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.44,0:46:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们四个人既没有通知我 也没有得到我的允许\N{\rEN}The four of you have involved me in an illegal activity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.61,0:46:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就把我卷进了一桩非法活动 我可不喜欢这样\N{\rEN}without my knowledge or consent, and I don't fucking appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.18,0:46:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没必要参与 长官 - 我不参与才怪\N{\rEN}- You don't have to be a part of it, sir. - The hell I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.75,0:46:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,既然已经谈妥 我现在阻挠的话\N{\rEN}If I delay this now, after this agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.55,0:46:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只会进一步增加那孩子的生命危险\N{\rEN}I just further endanger the life of that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.32,0:46:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得我会这么做?\N{\rEN}Does that sound like something you expect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.26,0:46:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 长官\N{\rEN}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.43,0:46:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上次去谈判的是我 我会承担责任的\N{\rEN}I went in there. I'll accept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.16,0:46:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么也承担不了!\N{\rEN}You'll accept nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别在这里逞英雄 小子\N{\rEN}Don't come in here trying to get noble, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.00,0:46:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看那个纸条\N{\rEN}Let me see that note.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.01,0:47:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEN}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.38,0:47:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他想把我们分开\N{\rEN}He wants to separate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.45,0:47:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这纸条上说你们应该在东岸等阿曼达\N{\rEN}The note instructs you guys to be on the east side and wait for Amanda,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.25,0:47:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我和尼克带着钱去边上的空地\N{\rEN}me and Nick to be at the clearing by the edge with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.66,0:47:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一接到阿曼达 马上用对讲机通知我们\N{\rEN}Once Amanda's turned over to you, you give us a call on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.53,0:47:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就给钱\N{\rEN}we turn over the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.76,0:47:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他可能带谁来? - 克里斯·穆伦\N{\rEN}- Who's he likely to bring with him? - Chris Mullen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.63,0:47:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们讨价还价时 他在那夜总会\N{\rEN}He was at the club when we made the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.83,0:47:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他有什么了解?\N{\rEN}What do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.54,0:47:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能是他替奶酪杀了雷\N{\rEN}It was probably him who killed Ray for Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.54,0:47:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我只能猜的话\N{\rEN}If I had to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.81,0:47:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 没有其他人知道这件事 对吗?\N{\rEN}All right. Nobody else knows about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道 - 唔?\N{\rEN}- I don't know. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.15,0:47:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问 这样私了 是对阿曼达更好 还是对我们更好?\N{\rEN}I'm asking if keeping it quiet is better for Amanda or is it better for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.58,0:47:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你有孩子吗 杰纳罗小姐?\N{\rEN}Do you have any children, Miss Gennaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.69,0:47:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没 长官\N{\rEN}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.76,0:47:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的独生女被杀了 她才12岁 你听说过吗?\N{\rEN}My only child was murdered. She was 12. Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.06,0:47:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有些东西你可能没有听过\N{\rEN}What you probably didn't hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.36,0:47:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望你永远不用面对\N{\rEN}and what I hope you never have to deal with,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.67,0:47:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是那种事情给人的感受 杰纳罗小姐 那是我不得不面对的\N{\rEN}Miss Gennaro, is what that feels like. What I have to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.97,0:48:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明明知道我的小女儿可能死\N{\rEN}Knowing that my little girl likely died
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.77,0:48:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哭喊着要我去救她\N{\rEN}crying out for me to come and save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.34,0:48:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有去\N{\rEN}And I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.71,0:48:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小女儿怀着惧怕 孤零零地死在一条浅水沟的边上\N{\rEN}My little girl died afraid and alone in a shallow ditch bank
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.05,0:48:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就在离我家不到10分钟远的路边\N{\rEN}by the side of the road not 10 minutes from my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.03,0:48:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道失去一个孩子是什么感觉\N{\rEN}I know what it feels like to lose a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.50,0:48:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 该死的 你们逼我出手\N{\rEN}Now, damn it, you force my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.74,0:48:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还怀疑我的处理方式\N{\rEN}and then you question the way I handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.10,0:48:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人怀疑你 长官\N{\rEN}No one's questioning you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.37,0:48:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我组建这个部门就是为了纪念孩子\N{\rEN}I honor my child with this division.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.34,0:48:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让别的父母经历我的遭遇\N{\rEN}So that no parent has to go through what I've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.31,0:48:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子\N{\rEN}This child.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.29,0:48:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就是我关心的一切\N{\rEN}That's all I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.86,0:48:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把她带回家\N{\rEN}I'm gonna bring her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.67,0:49:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他让我们大老远地到这里?\N{\rEN}Why'd he bring us all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.48,0:49:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 这里很大 很暗 容易逃跑\N{\rEN}I don't know. It's big. It's dark. It's easy to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.15,0:49:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.88,0:49:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打算杀了她\N{\rEN}They're gonna kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.24,0:49:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这些混蛋应该上别的地方找些平地\N{\rEN}This asshole could've found some level fucking ground somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.45,0:49:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就在这里分开 你们要到悬崖顶上\N{\rEN}This is where we part ways. You guys'll be on top of that cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.55,0:49:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就在你们对面\N{\rEN}We'll be right across from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.65,0:49:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们接到她就用对讲机通知我们\N{\rEN}Give us a call on the radio when you have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.79,0:50:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 会的 - 好的 好运\N{\rEN}- We will. - Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.20,0:50:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\rEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.47,0:50:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要怎么把阿曼达带上来?\N{\rEN}How are they gonna get Amanda up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.67,0:50:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有埋伏!有埋伏!\N{\rEN}Ambush! Ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.51,0:50:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 瑞米!该死的奶酪! 她在哪?\N{\rEN}Hey, Remy! Fucking Cheese! Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.55,0:51:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那 我看到她了 不该这样的!\N{\rEN}There she is. I can see her. It ain't the way it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.99,0:51:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有人打中了奶酪!\N{\rEN}Someone hit Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.76,0:51:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定你听到什么了? - 是的!\N{\rEN}- You sure you heard something? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.22,0:51:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在那里! - 发生了什么?\N{\rEN}- Over there! - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.86,0:51:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我听到水花四溅 在下面!\N{\rEN}I don't know. I heard a splash. Down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.63,0:51:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有人打死了奶酪\N{\rEN}Somebody took Cheese out,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.70,0:51:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后就乱成一锅粥了 - 阿曼达在哪里?\N{\rEN}- and then all hell broke loose. - Where's Amanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.20,0:51:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人从那里开的枪 - 我不知道!\N{\rEN}- Shots were fired from over there. - I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.43,0:51:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西掉水里了\N{\rEN}Something went in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.53,0:51:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 你确定你听到了?\N{\rEN}- What? - You sure you heard something?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.60,0:51:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 有东西掉进去了 但我… - 它去哪了?\N{\rEN}- Yeah, something went in, but I... - Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.00,0:51:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那里!就在那!\N{\rEN}There! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.54,0:51:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\rEN}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.77,0:51:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不\N{\rEN}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.15,0:51:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\rEN}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.94,0:52:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫高斯本医生 高斯本医生请移步重症监护室\N{\rEN}Paging Dr. Goldsburn. Dr. Goldsburn to ICU.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.59,0:52:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嗨\N{\rEN}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.06,0:52:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 腿怎么样? - 还好\N{\rEN}- How's the leg? - It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.94,0:53:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找到什么了吗?\N{\rEN}They find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.01,0:53:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 潜水员正在那里找 - 她可能还活着\N{\rEN}- They got divers in there now. - She could still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.88,0:53:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她躲起来了 她可能吓得不敢动\N{\rEN}Maybe she's hiding. She could be stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.79,0:53:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗?\N{\rEN}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.52,0:53:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不是\N{\rEN}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.04,0:53:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿…\N{\rEN}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.11,0:53:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要它存在一天 就会继续看护着\N{\rEN}He's ever seen in all his years,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.28,0:53:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫阿曼达的小女孩和 一个叫米拉贝尔的布娃娃\N{\rEN}on a little girl called Amanda and a doll named Mirabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.35,0:53:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个采石场的水潭深不见底 凶险莫测\N{\rEN}This quarry is extremely deep and treacherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.19,0:53:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被它吞噬的东西往往是永远沉沦其中\N{\rEN}All too often, she keeps that which she takes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.63,0:53:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一个悲惨的结局 苏珊\N{\rEN}A sad end to that story, Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.43,0:53:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是 菲尔\N{\rEN}It sure is, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.33,0:54:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来由罗恩报道体育新闻 今晚棕熊队有比赛吗?\N{\rEN}And Ron is next with sports. The Bruins in action tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.60,0:54:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 菲尔\N{\rEN}Yes, they are, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.10,0:54:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,棕熊队今晚挑战飞人队\N{\rEN}The B's took a crack at the Flyers tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.00,0:54:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,双方从第一节开始就杀得难分难解\N{\rEN}and the rough stuff started in the first period.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.21,0:54:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 她没了\N{\rEN}And like that, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.08,0:54:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们交待了自己知道的情况 尼克和瑞米也一样\N{\rEN}We gave our statements. Nick and Remy the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.62,0:54:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都没有为阿曼达的死受到责备\N{\rEN}All of us spared any blame for Amanda's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.15,0:54:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·道伊尔辞了职 他为此提出的条件是\N{\rEN}Jack Doyle resigned on the condition
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.12,0:54:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让他一个人承担所有责任\N{\rEN}that he and he alone be held accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.33,0:54:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,致力于救助儿童的传奇警监\N{\rEN}The legendary captain of a unit dedicated to children
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.10,0:54:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在一番争论后引退了\N{\rEN}stepped down today in the aftermath of controversy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.83,0:54:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他被授予提早退休的资格\N{\rEN}He was granted the dignity of early retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.04,0:54:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但代价是退休金减半\N{\rEN}But the humiliation of half a pension.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.81,0:54:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对于辉煌半生的他来说 这是个难堪的结局\N{\rEN}It was an ignominious end to an illustrious career.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.91,0:54:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,据他们说 克里斯在逃跑一天半后\N{\rEN}Chris' run lasted a day and a half until, from what they could tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.62,0:54:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了一个比他更需要钱的人\N{\rEN}he ran into someone who wanted the money more than he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.69,0:54:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯·穆伦 29岁\N{\rEN}Twenty-nine-year-old Chris Mullen
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.76,0:54:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚被枪杀\N{\rEN}was gunned down last night
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.89,0:55:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,原因显然是遭遇抢劫\N{\rEN}in an apparent robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.52,0:55:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,警方负责人辩解说 最近层出不穷的罪案\N{\rEN}The police commissioner defended the rising tide of crime
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.86,0:55:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是失业率和湿度上升引起的\N{\rEN}as a statistical aberration tied to growing unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.80,0:55:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,统计意义上的反常现象…\N{\rEN}and the humidity of...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.77,0:55:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在觉得时间够长以后 他们中止了搜寻工作\N{\rEN}Enough time went by and they called off the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.77,0:55:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给海琳发了死亡证明\N{\rEN}They issued Helene a death certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.16,0:55:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,像框和小棺材是殡仪馆捐赠的\N{\rEN}The frame and the casket were donated by the funeral home,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.86,0:55:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在黄昏前要归还\N{\rEN}but had to be returned at the end of the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.60,0:55:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我爱你 对吗?\N{\rEN}You know I love you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.71,0:55:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.41,0:55:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想一个人呆一会儿\N{\rEN}I just wanna be alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.35,0:56:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道她是责怪我还是责怪自己\N{\rEN}I don't know if she blamed me or if she blamed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.16,0:56:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 当她以为我不在家时\N{\rEN}But when she didn't think I was home,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.00,0:56:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是她以为我听不见时\N{\rEN}or if she thought I couldn't hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.60,0:56:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她会啜泣\N{\rEN}she would cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.84,0:56:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我情不自禁地在脑海中 一遍又一遍回想这件事\N{\rEN}I couldn't stop running it over and over and over in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.88,0:56:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,朦胧而依稀地怀疑着\N{\rEN}the vague and distant suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.65,0:56:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许从来没有弄明白那晚的事情\N{\rEN}that we never understood what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.69,0:56:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以及我们是什么角色\N{\rEN}what our role was.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.32,0:56:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或者事情就是这样 就像每年数以百计的\N{\rEN}Or maybe it was just that, like the hundreds of other children
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.73,0:56:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,人间蒸发的孩童一样\N{\rEN}who disappear each year and never return...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.80,0:56:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再也找不到的阿曼达 愈加萦绕在人们心头\N{\rEN}Amanda was even more haunting for never being found.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.54,0:57:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真正被他们找到的 是又一条大新闻\N{\rEN}What they did find was another big story,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.24,0:57:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不禁觉得很奇怪\N{\rEN}and I couldn't help but find it strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.61,0:57:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不到两个月 就在不远的地方 又有一个孩子失踪了\N{\rEN}Not two months later and not far away, another child went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.69,0:57:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…社区巡逻队成立了\N{\rEN}...and community watch patrols are being formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.49,0:57:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一辆自行车被丢在路边 一个轮子不停地转\N{\rEN}A bicycle left roadside. A tire left spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.56,0:57:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最新消息\N{\rEN}Late-breaking news on that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.46,0:57:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,记者相信\N{\rEN}Little Johnny Pietro is also wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.83,0:57:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小强尼·彼特罗的着装有标记\N{\rEN}what this reporter believes might be a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.33,0:57:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他戴着一个圣克里斯托弗的徽章\N{\rEN}Johnny Pietro was wearing the medallion of St. Christopher,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.03,0:57:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是守护圣徒…\N{\rEN}patron saint of...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.24,0:57:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼·彼特罗和他的徽章\N{\rEN}Johnny Pietro and his medallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.37,0:57:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不奇怪的是\N{\rEN}What I didn't find strange was this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.14,0:57:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次没有他的亲戚来敲我的门\N{\rEN}no relatives came knocking on our door.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.38,0:57:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 帕特里克 - 嗨\N{\rEN}- Hey, Patrick. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.92,0:57:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要你开车跟我来 - 去哪?\N{\rEN}- I need you to come on a ride with me. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.95,0:57:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到埃弗雷特\N{\rEN}To Everett.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.76,0:57:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 在林恩没有聚会吗? - 真好笑\N{\rEN}- What, no parties in Lynn? - Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.02,0:57:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你带着你的家伙吧 对吗? - 我的什么?\N{\rEN}- You got your toast with you, right? - My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.33,0:57:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的枪 傻瓜\N{\rEN}Your gun, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.06,0:57:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.51,0:58:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不是林恩的脱衣舞俱乐部 帕特里克\N{\rEN}This ain't no strip-clubbing in Lynn, Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.85,0:58:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我有更好的给你 伙计\N{\rEN}I got something better for you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.66,0:58:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我帮你找些人\N{\rEN}You asked me to find some people for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.76,0:58:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我找到他们了\N{\rEN}I think I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.73,0:58:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带我进什么地方?\N{\rEN}What you getting me into?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.87,0:58:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不再追查科温·厄尔了吗?\N{\rEN}You don't give a fuck about this Corwin Earle dude no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.94,0:58:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个肥婊子和那个老甲鱼就在那里\N{\rEN}Yo, 'cause the fat bitch and the old dude are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.27,0:58:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人不知道那个恋童癖的下落\N{\rEN}My man didn't know about the diddler.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.28,0:58:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起进去 给我打掩护\N{\rEN}Come in with me. Watch my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.98,0:58:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会查明那个王八蛋是不是也在\N{\rEN}We'll find out if this motherfucker's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.92,0:58:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 帕特里克?\N{\rEN}You know what, Patrick?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想进去 你不必进去\N{\rEN}If you don't wanna come in, you don't have to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.72,0:58:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想进去 就算了\N{\rEN}If you don't wanna come in, fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.09,0:58:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.12,0:59:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,猜下是谁?\N{\rEN}Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.69,0:59:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰罗姆·米勒? - 不 是白粉大仙来了\N{\rEN}- Jerome Miller? - No, it's the coke fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.62,0:59:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开门 - 我的钱在这里\N{\rEN}- Open up. - I got the money right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.53,0:59:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老狗 你想在这该死的门口给我钱?\N{\rEN}Marmaduke, you think you're gonna hand me money on a fucking porch?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.86,0:59:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rEN}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.70,0:59:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\rEN}Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.17,0:59:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你老爹 快开门!\N{\rEN}He's your father. Open the fucking door!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.07,0:59:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当心 - 好 伙计!\N{\rEN}- Look out. - Okay, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.24,0:59:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别激动!别激动!\N{\rEN}Chill! Chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.55,0:59:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们成立了一支乐队?\N{\rEN}What are you guys, starting a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.62,0:59:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人成立乐队\N{\rEN}No one's starting a band.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.86,1:00:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,试下这个\N{\rEN}It's a taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.56,1:00:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老头用的可卡因\N{\rEN}Cocaine for the old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.67,1:00:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rEN}Fucking Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.44,1:00:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要我帮你把这些零钱换成整的?\N{\rEN}Want me to change a roll of quarters for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.91,1:00:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 他们来这的时候要跟我说\N{\rEN}I told you to tell me when they got here!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.61,1:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们刚来\N{\rEN}They just got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.35,1:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你已经吸了一些 - 这是给我尝味道的\N{\rEN}- You already did some! - It was a taste bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.38,1:00:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 亲爱的\N{\rEN}Sorry, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.68,1:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,数一下这叠钱\N{\rEN}Here, count this fucking mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.12,1:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的在哪 伙计?\N{\rEN}Where's the rest, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.33,1:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他数完你给我的钱就给你\N{\rEN}As soon as he's finished counting that fucking mess you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.21,1:00:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 米勒先生 对不起? - 没关系\N{\rEN}- Mr. Miller, do you mind? - No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.61,1:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰你一下! - 你已经打扰了\N{\rEN}- Excuse me! - You're excused.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.21,1:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 请不要到处乱晃 先生 - 嘿 帅哥 别在意\N{\rEN}- Hey, please don't snoop around, sir. - Hey, relax, handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.35,1:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起!\N{\rEN}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.62,1:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是要去哪里?\N{\rEN}Where the fuck you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.25,1:01:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,米勒先生 我警告你!\N{\rEN}Mr. Miller, I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.69,1:01:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,停下!\N{\rEN}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.86,1:01:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克 开枪打她\N{\rEN}Patrick, shoot this bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.67,1:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你个肥婊子\N{\rEN}You fat busted cunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.01,1:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你既然用枪指着我 最好有胆开枪\N{\rEN}You put a gun on me, you better use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.78,1:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把白粉给我!\N{\rEN}Just give us the fucking wizza!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.88,1:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想开枪打她吗 帕特里克?\N{\rEN}You don't wanna shoot her, Patrick?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.16,1:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人是谁?\N{\rEN}Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.42,1:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,科温!回你的房间去\N{\rEN}Corwin! Go back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.09,1:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是聚会吗?\N{\rEN}It's not a party?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.23,1:01:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是聚会\N{\rEN}No, it's not a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.64,1:01:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少钱 帕特里克?\N{\rEN}How much money's there, Patrick?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.54,1:01:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\rEN}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.41,1:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这个?\N{\rEN}Want this?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.25,1:02:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?拿好钱\N{\rEN}What are you doing? Pick up the fucking money.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.53,1:02:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,房子里至少两支枪 罗伯塔的枪是随身带着的\N{\rEN}At least two guns in the house. Roberta's carrying hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.93,1:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有什么? - 他们很兴奋\N{\rEN}- What else? - Well, they're definitely high.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.26,1:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么? - 因为可卡因\N{\rEN}- On what? - Cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.27,1:02:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是你朋友告诉你的?\N{\rEN}Your friend tell you that, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.30,1:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,特警小组5分钟后到\N{\rEN}SWAT'll be here in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.87,1:02:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不打算等他们?\N{\rEN}You're not gonna wait for them?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.14,1:02:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有告诉我你看见科温·厄尔\N{\rEN}Did you or did you not tell me you saw Corwin Earle
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.31,1:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,手腕上戴着圣克里斯托弗的徽章?\N{\rEN}with the medallion of St. Christopher around his fucking wrist?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.24,1:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实看到了科温·厄尔\N{\rEN}I definitely saw Corwin Earle.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.64,1:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能等了\N{\rEN}We're not waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.78,1:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在这 不要乱动 好吗?\N{\rEN}Stay here. And don't fuck around, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.55,1:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\rEN}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.93,1:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rEN}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.51,1:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个…警官…有人开枪! 一个警官被击倒…枪击…\N{\rEN}An... An officer... Shots are fired! An officer down... Shots...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.78,1:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说!\N{\rEN}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.95,1:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一个警官在日耳曼路33号遭到枪击!\N{\rEN}A police officer has been shot at 33 German Road!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.30,1:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 别碰他!\N{\rEN}Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.32,1:05:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个意外\N{\rEN}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.77,1:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是意外\N{\rEN}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.18,1:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下!\N{\rEN}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.25,1:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.09,1:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧?\N{\rEN}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.12,1:07:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我发生了什么\N{\rEN}They told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.60,1:07:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你感到骄傲\N{\rEN}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.47,1:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人杀了一个孩子\N{\rEN}That man killed a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.17,1:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他没权活着\N{\rEN}He had no right to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.95,1:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你为我感到骄傲? - 当然\N{\rEN}- You're proud of me? - Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.38,1:08:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了你该做的\N{\rEN}You did what you had to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.99,1:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\rEN}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.93,1:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在这呆一会儿\N{\rEN}I gotta stay here awhile.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.17,1:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我回家等你 - 好\N{\rEN}- See you at home. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.39,1:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.60,1:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一团糟 对吗?\N{\rEN}It was fucked up, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.10,1:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们和你说过尼克的情况吗?\N{\rEN}They tell you anything about Nick?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.87,1:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说他会没事\N{\rEN}They said he could be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.51,1:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.48,1:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说那个男孩多大?\N{\rEN}They say how old that little boy was?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.38,1:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,7岁\N{\rEN}Seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.55,1:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,二年级\N{\rEN}Second grade.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.42,1:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该感到自豪 大部分人只会呆在外面\N{\rEN}Should be proud of yourself. Most guys would've stayed outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.89,1:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.70,1:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道什么?\N{\rEN}What don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.23,1:09:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的神父告诉我 羞耻就是上帝说你做错了\N{\rEN}My priest says shame is God telling you what you did was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.04,1:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\rEN}Fuck him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.37,1:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人是罪\N{\rEN}Murder's a sin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.08,1:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要看你杀的是谁\N{\rEN}Depends on who you do it to.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.85,1:09:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是不择手段 只求结果\N{\rEN}That's not how it works. It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.26,1:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经栽赃陷害过一个人\N{\rEN}I planted evidence on a guy once,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.43,1:10:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在95年\N{\rEN}back in '95.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.57,1:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每缴获三克半毒品 就给线人100美元\N{\rEN}We were paying $ 100 an eight-ball to snitches.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.04,1:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友雷·利堪斯基 给我们打了个电话\N{\rEN}We got a call from our pal, Ray Likanski.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.81,1:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当时他找不到可以揭发的人了\N{\rEN}He couldn't find enough guys to rat out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 他告诉我们 在哥伦比亚角那边\N{\rEN}Anyway, he tells us there's a guy pumping up in an apartment
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.31,1:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人在公寓里卖白粉\N{\rEN}up in Columbia Point.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.32,1:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去了 我和尼克\N{\rEN}We go in, me and Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.42,1:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,15年前 尼克上阵的时候 可不是开玩笑的\N{\rEN}Fifteen years ago, when Nicky went in, it was no joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.09,1:10:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那里…是个仓库一样的房子\N{\rEN}So, it's a... It's a stash house, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.92,1:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个老太婆被打翻在地 她丈夫很卑鄙 突然出现\N{\rEN}The old lady's beat to shit, the husband's mean, cracked out,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.90,1:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想给我们制造麻烦 尼克把他撂倒\N{\rEN}tries to give us trouble, Nicky lays him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.67,1:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搜查了一下 但是感觉我们是搞错了\N{\rEN}We're doing an inventory, but it looks like we messed up
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.73,1:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为屋里没有毒品 接着我走进了后面的房间\N{\rEN}because there's no dope in the house, and I go in the back room...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.14,1:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说明一下 那个地方像狗窝\N{\rEN}Now, this place was a shithole, mind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.74,1:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老鼠 蟑螂都处都是\N{\rEN}Rats, roaches all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.45,1:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在后面 孩子的卧室里\N{\rEN}But the kid's room, in the back,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.92,1:11:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,却一尘不染\N{\rEN}was spotless.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.59,1:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我是说 他经常打扫 拖地 干净得无可挑剔\N{\rEN}No, I mean, he swept it, mopped it, it was immaculate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.29,1:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小男孩坐在床上\N{\rEN}The little boy's sitting on the bed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.63,1:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,死死抱着他的PlayStation\N{\rEN}holding onto his PlayStation for dear life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.16,1:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,脸上毫无表情\N{\rEN}There's no expression on his face,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.23,1:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,眼泪流个不停\N{\rEN}tears streaming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.77,1:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他想告诉我他刚学会九九乘法表\N{\rEN}He wants to tell me he just learned his multiplication tables.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.74,1:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEN}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.98,1:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 他父亲把他扔在一个狗窝里\N{\rEN}I mean, the father's got him in this crack den,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.65,1:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只给他吃小蛋糕 还打他屁股\N{\rEN}subsisting on Twinkies and ass-whippings,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.41,1:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子仅仅希望有人夸他干得不错\N{\rEN}and this little boy just wants someone to tell him that he's doing a good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.12,1:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你对天主教感到过疑惑吗?\N{\rEN}You're worried what's Catholic?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.59,1:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 孩子们只会宽恕\N{\rEN}I mean, kids forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.63,1:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们不会审判\N{\rEN}Kids don't judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.03,1:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们把另一边脸也给你打\N{\rEN}Kids turn the other cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.47,1:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这样做 得到的是什么?\N{\rEN}What do they get for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.27,1:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我走了回去\N{\rEN}So I went back out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.67,1:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我在起居室的地板上放了一盎司海洛因\N{\rEN}I put an ounce of heroin on the living room floor,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.84,1:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我把那个当爸爸的送去坐牢 七到九年\N{\rEN}and I sent the father on a ride, seven to nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.45,1:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那样做对吗? - 太他妈对了\N{\rEN}- That was the right thing? - Fucking A!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.79,1:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你总得选一边\N{\rEN}You gotta take a side.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.82,1:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你猥亵儿童 殴打儿童\N{\rEN}You molest a child, you beat a child,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.13,1:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不是我这一边的\N{\rEN}you're not on my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.73,1:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你看见我来 你最好跑\N{\rEN}If you see me coming, you better run,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.27,1:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要干死你\N{\rEN}because I am gonna lay you the fuck down!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.74,1:12:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放松\N{\rEN}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.41,1:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得轻松\N{\rEN}Don't feel easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.21,1:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有父亲 这个孩子是不是过得更好?\N{\rEN}Is the kid better off without his father?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.52,1:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.42,1:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 说不定他正在贩毒\N{\rEN}But okay, I mean, could be out there right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.66,1:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,腰里还插着把手枪\N{\rEN}pumping with a gun in his waistband.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.89,1:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场战争 伙计\N{\rEN}It's a war, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.13,1:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们占了上风吗?\N{\rEN}Are we winning?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.37,1:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.87,1:13:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你还会再做一次吗? 会打死科温·厄尔吗?\N{\rEN}Would you do it again? Clip Corwin Earle?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.81,1:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.65,1:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那样你就对了吗?\N{\rEN}Does that make you right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.42,1:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\rEN}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.52,1:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.89,1:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那样也不能算错 对吗?\N{\rEN}Doesn't make it wrong, though, does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.14,1:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N{\rEN}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.31,1:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米怎么样?\N{\rEN}How's Remy?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.55,1:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了我\N{\rEN}He lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.55,1:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,以前跟瑞米提起雷的时候 他怎么说?\N{\rEN}What did Remy say about Ray back in Roxbury?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.32,1:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 从没听说过他 - 从没听说过他\N{\rEN}- Never heard of him. - Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.23,1:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他说雷向他告密有15年了\N{\rEN}Now he says Ray's been snitching for him for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.56,1:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫他老朋友\N{\rEN}He called him his "old pal."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.63,1:14:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还说他都找不到可以揭发的人了\N{\rEN}Said he couldn't find enough people to snitch out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.57,1:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克…\N{\rEN}Patrick...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.87,1:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都是由于雷·利堪斯基 阿曼达才被抓\N{\rEN}And Ray Likanski is the reason Amanda got taken in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.94,1:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米撒谎说不认识他\N{\rEN}and Remy lies about knowing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.18,1:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\rEN}Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.75,1:14:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么要撒谎? 他要隐瞒什么?\N{\rEN}Why would he lie? What's he have to hide?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.35,1:14:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达死了\N{\rEN}Amanda's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.88,1:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\rEN}Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.56,1:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\rEN}Babe.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.50,1:14:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克死了\N{\rEN}Nick died.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.81,1:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,左 左\N{\rEN}Left. Left.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.19,1:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯奇先生\N{\rEN}Mr. Kenzie.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.49,1:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,科温·厄尔那件事 你干得好\N{\rEN}Nice fucking job on Corwin Earle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.24,1:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\rEN}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.71,1:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关于尼克 请节哀 - 好 谢谢\N{\rEN}- Sorry about Nick. - Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.61,1:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了想那天晚上我们的对话\N{\rEN}I was thinking about our conversation the other night.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.18,1:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了些不该说的\N{\rEN}Well, I said some things I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.42,1:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我喝多了\N{\rEN}You know, too much rum.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.09,1:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哪些话你不该说?\N{\rEN}Yeah, like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.39,1:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不要烦我 帕特里克\N{\rEN}Don't fuck with me, Patrick. Not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.30,1:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我不想找你麻烦\N{\rEN}Oh, I wouldn't fuck with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.70,1:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你想这样玩?好吧\N{\rEN}Oh, you wanna play it like that, huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.17,1:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了那晚的事 我们会成为朋友\N{\rEN}Forget about the other night, and we'll be friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.34,1:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不呢?\N{\rEN}What if I don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.51,1:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是一个你想要的"如果"\N{\rEN}That's not an "if" you wanna bring into your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.12,1:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上周和他吃了饭\N{\rEN}Had lunch with him last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.59,1:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,达纳上周和他吃了饭?\N{\rEN}Dana had lunch with him last week?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.82,1:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪了\N{\rEN}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.99,1:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 德弗\N{\rEN}Hey, Dev.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.56,1:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 如何? - 很好 你呢?\N{\rEN}- Hey, how you doing? - All right, how you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.06,1:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\rEN}I can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.27,1:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能和你聊几句吗? - 可以\N{\rEN}- Can I talk to you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.70,1:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不方便\N{\rEN}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.64,1:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样 那你要请我吃午饭了\N{\rEN}If it's like that, then you're gonna have to buy me lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.11,1:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去查特豪斯餐馆吧 半小时后? - 可以\N{\rEN}- How's the Chart House, half hour? - Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.75,1:17:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 瑞米原来和你一起缉毒 对吗?\N{\rEN}Hey, Remy used to work Narcotics with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.72,1:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,DCU（缉毒部门） 对 怎么了?\N{\rEN}DCU, yeah. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.48,1:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么离开?\N{\rEN}Why'd he leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.09,1:17:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他老是会把别人惹毛\N{\rEN}Had a habit of just rubbing people the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.72,1:17:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说?他做了什么?\N{\rEN}Like what? What'd he do?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.86,1:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比如 和一个妓女结婚\N{\rEN}Like marry a prostitute, for one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.39,1:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\rEN}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.56,1:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是警察 不可能做这种事 对吗?\N{\rEN}Might not wanna do that if you're a cop, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.33,1:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你是水管工 也不可能做这种事\N{\rEN}Might not wanna do that if you're a plumber.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.10,1:17:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 发生了什么?\N{\rEN}So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.87,1:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他爱她 叫迈克·斯耐尔别管闲事\N{\rEN}He says he loves her, tells Mike Snell to go fuck himself,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.64,1:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就申请了转调\N{\rEN}and puts in for a transfer.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.81,1:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 调到道伊尔那里?\N{\rEN}What, to Doyle?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.91,1:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,72年 是道伊尔把 瑞米从路易斯安那带过来的\N{\rEN}Doyle brought Remy from Louisiana, back in '72.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.68,1:17:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你不认为瑞米有污点 是吗?\N{\rEN}You don't think that Remy's dirty, though, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.18,1:17:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么污点?\N{\rEN}What's "dirty"?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.62,1:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道他有次栽赃害人 - 哦 你知道?\N{\rEN}- I know he planted evidence once. - Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.52,1:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对 怎么?\N{\rEN}Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.53,1:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 伙计 CSI这部电视剧 可把我们害惨了\N{\rEN}Look, man. CSI is killing us out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.16,1:17:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,每个陪审员 都希望我们找到微纤维啥的\N{\rEN}Every other juror, all they wanna know is where the microfibers are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.77,1:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是干活的\N{\rEN}Certain people are workers.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.63,1:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不想栽赃 你也要知道怎么做\N{\rEN}Don't wanna plant it, but you know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.34,1:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们不介意\N{\rEN}So they don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.51,1:18:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你打听他干什么?\N{\rEN}So tell me something, what you fucking with him for?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.68,1:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他骗了我\N{\rEN}He lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.15,1:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不出他有什么理由要骗我\N{\rEN}I can't think of one reason big enough for him to lie
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.48,1:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他骗我的是无关紧要的小事\N{\rEN}that's small enough not to matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.09,1:18:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 瞧\N{\rEN}All right, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.83,1:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道一件事 但也是听说的 你可以听一下\N{\rEN}I know one thing, but it's third party, so you gotta play it like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.36,1:18:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳和雷在6月吞了奶酪的钱 对吗?\N{\rEN}Helene and Ray took Cheese's money back in June, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.47,1:18:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.57,1:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一周后 瑞米来到DCU问一个警员\N{\rEN}One week later, Remy goes to a cop in DCU
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.60,1:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有人知道是谁吞了奶酪的钱\N{\rEN}asking if anybody knew who robbed Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.14,1:18:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢?\N{\rEN}So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.41,1:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼线告诉我\N{\rEN}So my informant tells me,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.24,1:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,奶酪过了两周才知道他的钱被吞了\N{\rEN}Cheese didn't even know he got robbed until two weeks later.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.05,1:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么瑞米比奶酪先知道 他的钱被吞了?\N{\rEN}So Remy knew Cheese got robbed before Cheese did?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.98,1:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么知道的?\N{\rEN}How'd he know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.05,1:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你\N{\rEN}Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.92,1:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在你开始东奔西走调查警察之前\N{\rEN}You better think long and hard
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.06,1:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好认真地想一想\N{\rEN}before you start running around here investigating the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.13,1:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你从他们口中夺食 他们会要你的命\N{\rEN}You try and take food out their mouths, and they will fuck you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.57,1:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的牛排\N{\rEN}Thanks for the steak.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.14,1:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢\N{\rEN}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.28,1:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.72,1:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\rEN}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.86,1:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话和你说 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}We need to talk to you, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.86,1:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,关于什么?\N{\rEN}About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.36,1:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你房间的隔音效果\N{\rEN}About the acoustics in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.16,1:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.80,1:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我们也住在三层公寓 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}Oh, we live in a three-decker, too, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.77,1:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么可说的\N{\rEN}I got nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.70,1:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好 不错 我们可以和州警说\N{\rEN}Well, that's fine. We can talk to the state police.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.91,1:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在默菲酒吧见我\N{\rEN}Meet me at Murphy's Law.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.49,1:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去默菲酒吧见他\N{\rEN}I don't meet him down Murphy's,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.09,1:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他会报警的\N{\rEN}he's gonna call the staties.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.46,1:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他在算计你 不要去那里\N{\rEN}He's putting a move on you. Don't go down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.43,1:20:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我能应付帕特里克·肯奇\N{\rEN}I can handle Patrick Kenzie.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.07,1:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我们发的誓 - 是我带头的\N{\rEN}- This is an oath we took. - I started this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.84,1:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要保护它 - 我也有要保护的东西\N{\rEN}- This has to be protected. - I got things to protect, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.87,1:20:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听我说! - 好的 瑞米\N{\rEN}- Listen to me! - All right, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.04,1:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是离开那间屋子 就是我的敌人\N{\rEN}You leave that house, you're an enemy to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.47,1:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 相信我 好吗? - 不!相信我\N{\rEN}- Just trust me, all right? - No! Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.88,1:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家乡 人们把秘密带到棺材里!\N{\rEN}Where I come from, you die with your secrets!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.77,1:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识瑞米多久了?\N{\rEN}How long have you known Remy?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.28,1:20:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,布里桑特侦探?就在…\N{\rEN}Detective Bressant? Just in...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.48,1:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达的调查中认识他的\N{\rEN}Met him through the investigation of Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.82,1:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这样? - 是的\N{\rEN}- That's it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.19,1:21:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识瑞米多久了?\N{\rEN}How long you known Remy?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.39,1:21:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干什么?\N{\rEN}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.66,1:21:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有互联网了 莱昂内尔\N{\rEN}They got the Internet, now, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.70,1:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道镇上的每个人相互都认识\N{\rEN}You know how it is in town. Everybody knows everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.13,1:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是每个人都相互认识\N{\rEN}No. Everybody don't know everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.67,1:21:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想说什么? - 你为什么撒谎?\N{\rEN}- What're you talking about? - Why you lying?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.37,1:21:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEN}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.44,1:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我们见面的第一天就撒了个弥天大谎\N{\rEN}You bragged about taking a hard bust on the first day we met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.27,1:21:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我没有 - 放屁\N{\rEN}- No, I didn't. - Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.91,1:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你隐瞒了一些事情 莱昂内尔 你最好说出来\N{\rEN}You're hiding something, Lionel, and you better fucking tell it,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.48,1:21:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是你来到我们家 要我们帮你\N{\rEN}'cause you came to our house and you asked us for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.48,1:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们千辛万苦去救阿曼达\N{\rEN}And we killed ourselves trying to save Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.78,1:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道你有事瞒着我\N{\rEN}And I know you ain't being 100% with me right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.68,1:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你撒的谎让我真的很生气\N{\rEN}and it's really fucking pissing me off that you're lying,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.69,1:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你最好快点打断我 我就要失去…\N{\rEN}so you better interrupt me at any time, 'cause I'm about to lose...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.22,1:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好 好 不要心脏病发作\N{\rEN}Okay. Fine, fine. All right? Don't have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.29,1:21:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有跟你说实话\N{\rEN}I haven't been honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.50,1:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是什么值得骄傲的事情\N{\rEN}It's just not something I'm proud of. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.53,1:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天我在酒吧斗殴\N{\rEN}I got in a bar fight back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.47,1:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对方的头骨被打破了\N{\rEN}The other guy cracked his skull.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.77,1:21:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在对打的时候 我肯定说过 "我要杀了你"\N{\rEN}At some point, I must've said, "I'll kill you."
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.34,1:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我因为故意伤害被捕 我交待的情节和对方不一样\N{\rEN}So they had me up for attempted. It's my word against this other guy's.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.78,1:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,目击者证实了我说的话 陪审团相信了他\N{\rEN}Witness testified to my version and the jury believed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.61,1:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为他是个警察 - 是的 他为我作证\N{\rEN}- 'Cause he was a cop. - Yeah, he testified for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.58,1:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这样认识了布里桑特侦探\N{\rEN}So you knew Detective Bressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.32,1:22:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们不是特别要好的朋友 - 但你撒了谎\N{\rEN}- It's not like we were best friends. - But you lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.69,1:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你为什么叫瑞米帮忙? - 他是个警察\N{\rEN}- Why did you call Remy? - He's a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.99,1:22:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那不是你叫他帮忙的原因 莱昂内尔 - 得了\N{\rEN}- That's not why you called him, Lionel. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.93,1:22:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你家地方很小 他们吵架你都听得见\N{\rEN}It's a small place. You heard them arguing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.86,1:22:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们吵得很响 - 谁?谁…谁…\N{\rEN}- They were being loud. - Who? Who... Who...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.53,1:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你叫了瑞米 你和他绑架阿曼达来勒索你妹妹\N{\rEN}So you called Remy, and you and him took Amanda to blackmail your sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.04,1:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要这么做?\N{\rEN}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.80,1:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 莱昂内尔 我真不知道\N{\rEN}I don't know, Lionel. I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.91,1:22:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为 虽然你"浪子回头"这么多年\N{\rEN}Maybe because after all the "I put the fucking plug in the jug,"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.98,1:22:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你又是"细数主恩" 又是"嘴上积德"\N{\rEN}and the "count your blessings" and the "watch your language,"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.05,1:22:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你还是和其他人一样\N{\rEN}you're just like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.28,1:22:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看到一袋钱就想得到它\N{\rEN}You saw a bag of money and you wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.25,1:22:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为可以逃过法网\N{\rEN}And you thought you could get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.92,1:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是碧通知了媒体 把事情搞大了\N{\rEN}But Bea called the media and made a big thing of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.12,1:22:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,接着她找了我们 你就傻眼了\N{\rEN}And then she called us, and then you were fucked.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.56,1:22:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个案子结了 帕特里克 这个案子结了\N{\rEN}The case is closed, Patrick. The case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.76,1:22:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,贩毒的海地人是栽赃的好对象\N{\rEN}Coke-dealing Haitian's a pretty easy target for a frame.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.13,1:22:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱昂内尔? - 劳驾\N{\rEN}- Lionel? - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.50,1:22:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看着我 - 好的 劳驾\N{\rEN}- Look at me. - Okay. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.63,1:22:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你抓了你的外甥女 然后嫁祸给一个黑人\N{\rEN}You took your niece, and you laid it off on a black guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.33,1:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 劳驾 - 莱昂内尔 告诉我发生了什么\N{\rEN}- Pardon me. - Lionel, tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.63,1:23:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,服务员能来一下吗?\N{\rEN}Can I get some service?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.84,1:23:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.98,1:23:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么?\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.98,1:23:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三杯顺风威士忌 一瓶tallboy - 好的\N{\rEN}- Three shots of Cutty and a tallboy. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.18,1:23:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.99,1:23:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想一下\N{\rEN}Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.29,1:23:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,二十三年不算短 对吗?\N{\rEN}Twenty-three years is something, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.83,1:24:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\rEN}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.34,1:24:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来照看阿曼达 她和往常一样孤单\N{\rEN}I come up to check on Amanda. She was alone as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.81,1:24:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳和雷回家时 我正给她讲故事\N{\rEN}I was reading her a story when Helene and Ray come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.42,1:24:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不知道我在那里\N{\rEN}They didn't know I was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.58,1:24:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别鬼叫了 我女儿在那里睡觉\N{\rEN}Stop fucking yelling, my daughter's sleeping in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.26,1:24:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们开始讲要怎样私吞那个毒贩的钱\N{\rEN}They started talking about how they'd robbed this drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.96,1:24:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果他发现了会做什么吗?\N{\rEN}You know what he's fucking gonna do if he finds out?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.13,1:24:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,钱怎么办?\N{\rEN}What's the monkey gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.96,1:24:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 你知道… - 我不…\N{\rEN}- Oh, you know... - I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.36,1:24:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说要离开这个州\N{\rEN}And they were talking about leaving the state.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.60,1:24:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我打电话给瑞米 告诉了他\N{\rEN}So I called Remy and told him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.13,1:24:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,另外一个毒贩到了纳舒厄 带着可卡因…\N{\rEN}There's another drug run up to Nashua. Taking cocaine...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.87,1:24:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢?\N{\rEN}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.31,1:24:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带走了她\N{\rEN}We took her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.28,1:24:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米定了这个计划 看上去很简单\N{\rEN}Remy laid out this plan. It seemed easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.08,1:24:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带走她 逼海琳和雷把钱吐出来\N{\rEN}We take her, force Helene and Ray to cough up the cash,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.02,1:25:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后放她回去\N{\rEN}then we put her back. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.12,1:25:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达在乡下度过一个周末\N{\rEN}Amanda gets to spend a weekend in the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.26,1:25:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹尝到一个教训\N{\rEN}My sister learns a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.13,1:25:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的 这样一来人人都有收获\N{\rEN}And fuck it, everybody gets paid on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.96,1:25:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拿奶酪这种人的钱我问心无愧\N{\rEN}I got no problem taking money from a guy like Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.00,1:25:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,警察那边有他们应付\N{\rEN}They were gonna handle the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.63,1:25:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 碧 她急疯了\N{\rEN}But Bea, she went nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.94,1:25:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,开始通知报纸 雇用你\N{\rEN}Started calling the papers. Hired you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.57,1:25:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莱昂内尔不希望我来这 现在你们还不想接这份工作?\N{\rEN}Lionel don't want me coming here, now you don't want the job?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.97,1:25:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你找到了钱 结果阿曼达和钱都在他们手里了\N{\rEN}But once you found the money, they had Amanda and the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.04,1:25:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们决定做一笔假交易给你看\N{\rEN}So they decided to set up a fake exchange for you to witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.25,1:25:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们买通克里斯·穆伦 在采石场陷害奶酪\N{\rEN}They got Chris Mullen to set up Cheese at the quarry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.98,1:25:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1万5千美金和一个当老大的机会\N{\rEN}15K and a chance to be the boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.39,1:25:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,奶酪明白了是怎么回事\N{\rEN}Cheese figured out what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.76,1:25:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然为时已晚 他还是开了枪\N{\rEN}Even though it was too late, he started shooting.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.30,1:25:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,慌乱中\N{\rEN}Panicking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.87,1:25:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她就掉下去了 我是说 她就…\N{\rEN}And she just fell. I mean, she just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.27,1:25:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,掉了下去\N{\rEN}She fell in.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.41,1:25:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她没了\N{\rEN}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.11,1:25:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一个意外 只是一个意外\N{\rEN}It was an accident. It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.38,1:25:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她是你妹妹的孩子\N{\rEN}She was your sister's kid, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.48,1:26:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你妹妹的孩子 - 你以为我不想她?\N{\rEN}- Your sister's child. - You think I don't miss her?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.22,1:26:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,比起海琳 她更像我的孩子\N{\rEN}She was more my kid than Helene's.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.89,1:26:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去年夏天 海琳和道蒂 带阿曼达去了海滩\N{\rEN}Last summer, Helene and Dottie took Amanda to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.16,1:26:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那天真的很热 阿曼达睡着了\N{\rEN}It was a real hot day. Amanda fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.73,1:26:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她们把她留在车里 自己奔向沙滩\N{\rEN}They left her in the car while they go off into the dunes,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.33,1:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和别人一起抽大麻\N{\rEN}smoke a doobie with some guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.17,1:26:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,两个小时\N{\rEN}Two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.64,1:26:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达差点被烤熟了\N{\rEN}Amanda literally roasted.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.61,1:26:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她才三岁\N{\rEN}She was three.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.88,1:26:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,后来 我抱着她 试图帮她入睡\N{\rEN}Later on, I was holding her, trying to help her get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.19,1:26:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小阿曼达 她太热了\N{\rEN}My little Amanda, she was so hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.09,1:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就像刚从炉子里出来的\N{\rEN}She felt like something just come out of the oven.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.40,1:26:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就像罐焖肉一样\N{\rEN}Like a fucking pot roast.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.83,1:26:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要替我妹妹难过\N{\rEN}So don't feel too sorry for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.24,1:27:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她除了自己从没关心过任何人\N{\rEN}Because she never gave a shit about anyone but herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.11,1:27:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 打开保险柜 快\N{\rEN}Bartender. Open the safe. Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.61,1:27:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都闭嘴 别吵 趴在地上 趴在地上!\N{\rEN}Everybody needs to shut up and stay calm. On the floor. On the floor!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.65,1:27:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 手抱头 快 - 哦 天哪\N{\rEN}- Hands on your head. Do it. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.39,1:27:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都要静下来 一分钟里完成\N{\rEN}Everybody stays calm, this'll be over in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.06,1:27:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你知道这个酒吧是谁的吗 混蛋?\N{\rEN}Hey, do you know whose bar this is, shithead?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.56,1:27:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以放聪明点 全看你的了\N{\rEN}Or you can get wise, it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.16,1:27:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说了什么?\N{\rEN}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.73,1:27:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢嚼舌头 嗯?\N{\rEN}You're a talker, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.84,1:27:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再说啊 他妈的\N{\rEN}Just keep revving, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.47,1:27:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,照他说的做 他有枪\N{\rEN}Don't antagonize him. He's got a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.64,1:27:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 继续说呵 - 我一个字也没说\N{\rEN}- Oh, just keep yapping away. - I didn't say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.04,1:27:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该学会闭嘴\N{\rEN}You should learn to keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.98,1:27:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上闭嘴吧\N{\rEN}Shut the fuck up, for Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.48,1:27:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再说啊 伙计 - 我一个字都没说\N{\rEN}- Just keep talking, pal. - I didn't say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.28,1:27:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,闭眼\N{\rEN}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.72,1:27:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死的 - 瑞米·布里桑特\N{\rEN}- Fuck! - Remy Bressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.92,1:27:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是瑞米·布里桑特绑架了 阿曼达·麦克雷蒂\N{\rEN}Amanda McCready was taken by Remy Bressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.32,1:27:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死的 天哪 是瑞米·布里桑特 绑架了阿曼达·麦克雷蒂\N{\rEN}Oh, fuck, God. Amanda McCready was taken by Remy Bressant!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.12,1:27:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等 上帝 - 瑞米·布里桑特\N{\rEN}- Wait. Wait. Jesus. - Remy Bressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.03,1:27:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的 瑞米·布里桑特!\N{\rEN}God damn it. Remy Bressant!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.66,1:27:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达·麦克雷蒂被绑架了\N{\rEN}Amanda McCready was taken
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.79,1:27:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞米·布里桑特干的 - 上帝啊 我告诉他了\N{\rEN}- by Remy Bressant. - Jesus. I told him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.00,1:27:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他我们为了勒索钱财绑架她 我告诉了他 我告诉了他 瑞米\N{\rEN}I told him we took her for ransom. I told him. I told him, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.57,1:28:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我告诉他为了勒索钱财绑架她 我已经说了\N{\rEN}Please, I told him we took her for ransom. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.07,1:28:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米 求你了\N{\rEN}Remy, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.17,1:28:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEN}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.92,1:28:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗?\N{\rEN}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.96,1:28:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和他呆在一块\N{\rEN}Stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.36,1:29:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,放下你的枪\N{\rEN}Drop your gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.86,1:29:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,放下!\N{\rEN}Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.30,1:29:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那伙计来真的\N{\rEN}That bartender wasn't fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.45,1:29:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么?\N{\rEN}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.85,1:29:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是你害死了她?\N{\rEN}Did you get her killed?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.22,1:30:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说是\N{\rEN}Say yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.89,1:30:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说是\N{\rEN}Say yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.16,1:30:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说是!\N{\rEN}Say yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.53,1:30:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么?打死我? 是 是 是\N{\rEN}What're you gonna do? Shoot me? Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.05,1:30:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个孩子\N{\rEN}She was a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.22,1:30:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢孩子\N{\rEN}I love children.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.96,1:31:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我要揭露我自己参与的阴谋?\N{\rEN}Why would I expose a conspiracy that I was a part of?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.96,1:31:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 莱昂内尔和我说的有矛盾吗?\N{\rEN}I mean, did Lionel contradict anything I've said?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.74,1:31:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧里其他目击者跟我说的有矛盾吗?\N{\rEN}Did any of the witnesses at the bar contradict anything I've said?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.04,1:31:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一个警官今天被杀了 这可不是小事\N{\rEN}A police officer was killed today. That's not looked on lightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.78,1:31:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,贪污腐败难道是小事?\N{\rEN}Is corruption looked on lightly?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.05,1:31:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小女孩被害死难道是小事?\N{\rEN}Is a little girl getting killed looked on lightly?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.78,1:31:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 冷静\N{\rEN}Whoa, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.08,1:31:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是收费的私人侦探\N{\rEN}You charge people money as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.58,1:31:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚上你在采石场 对吗?\N{\rEN}Now, you're at the quarry the other night, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.59,1:31:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道那是一个骗局?\N{\rEN}And you have no idea that this is a setup?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.59,1:31:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你被蒙在鼓里 对吗?\N{\rEN}You're baffled. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.53,1:31:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也许你觉得很奇怪 其实我上当是因为\N{\rEN}No, because, strange as it might seem,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.07,1:31:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,警察告诉我的事情我总是相信的\N{\rEN}I believe the police when they tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.00,1:31:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个菜鸟 你知道么?\N{\rEN}You're a fresh prick. You know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.30,1:31:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看到一张勒索的纸条 和阿曼达·麦克雷蒂的毯子\N{\rEN}And because I had a ransom note and Amanda McCready's blanket
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.61,1:32:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就放在我的邮箱里\N{\rEN}put in my mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.77,1:32:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看到一份电话记录 是奶酪打到警察局的\N{\rEN}And because I read a transcript of a call that Cheese put into the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.88,1:32:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一个911报警电话?\N{\rEN}A 911 call?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.05,1:32:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是奶酪打到警局的电话\N{\rEN}No, it was a call Cheese made to the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.18,1:32:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,打给在警局的瑞米·布里桑特\N{\rEN}To Remy Bressant at the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.55,1:32:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是克里斯·穆伦冒充奶酪打的\N{\rEN}Or that Chris Mullen made, pretending to be Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.69,1:32:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么 反正录下来了\N{\rEN}Or whatever the fuck it was, but it was recorded,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.55,1:32:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一个电话\N{\rEN}and there was a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.52,1:32:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会给打到警局的电话录音\N{\rEN}We don't record calls coming into the station,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.53,1:32:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不做文字记录 聪明人\N{\rEN}and we don't do transcripts, smart guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.43,1:32:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你听到磁带了?\N{\rEN}So, did you hear a tape?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.37,1:32:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我没有听到 - 好的\N{\rEN}- No, I didn't hear a tape. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.74,1:32:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到文字记录了?\N{\rEN}Did you see a transcript?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.71,1:32:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我肯定记错了\N{\rEN}No, I must've remembered it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.52,1:32:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们只会宽恕\N{\rEN}Kids forgive.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.06,1:32:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这样做 得到的是什么?\N{\rEN}What do they get for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.63,1:32:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达差点被烤熟了\N{\rEN}Amanda literally roasted.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.37,1:33:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我不想她?\N{\rEN}You think I don't miss her.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.64,1:33:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比起海琳 她更像我的孩子\N{\rEN}She was more my kid than Helene's.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.14,1:33:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢孩子\N{\rEN}I love children.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.78,1:33:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是你想做的事情 帕特里克 你要确定\N{\rEN}This is the kind of thing that if you do, Patrick, you wanna be sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.29,1:33:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗?\N{\rEN}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.72,1:33:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.96,1:33:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你来吗?\N{\rEN}Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.46,1:33:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.41,1:33:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,72年 是道伊尔把 瑞米从路易斯安那带过来的\N{\rEN}Doyle brought Remy from Louisiana back in '72.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.21,1:33:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,读读重点标出的那段好吗?\N{\rEN}Care to read the highlighted portion?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.59,1:34:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要去旅游?\N{\rEN}Taking a trip?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.00,1:34:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克·肯奇\N{\rEN}Patrick Kenzie.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.37,1:34:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么不能去开心一下?\N{\rEN}To what do I owe the pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.24,1:34:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米·布里桑特昨晚死了\N{\rEN}Remy Bressant died last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.41,1:34:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了 那很不光彩\N{\rEN}I was told. It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.88,1:34:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 很难理解 因为他看上去像个好人\N{\rEN}Yeah, it's hard to understand. Because he seemed like a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.55,1:34:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\N{\rEN}He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.72,1:34:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道人们为何行事\N{\rEN}We don't know why people do what they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.72,1:34:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都从自己的那扇窗看出去\N{\rEN}Everybody looks out his own window.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.29,1:34:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有自己的理由\N{\rEN}And everyone's got their reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.87,1:34:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N{\rEN}- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.64,1:34:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗? - 很好\N{\rEN}- How are you? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.01,1:34:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克 他们正在向我开火\N{\rEN}Nick! They're firing at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.14,1:34:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克 你听得见我说话吗?你还好吗? 他们正在向我开火\N{\rEN}Nick, you hear me? You okay? They're firing at me!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.91,1:34:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞米!\N{\rEN}Remy!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.15,1:34:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我听见有东西掉进水里了! - 有埋伏!有埋伏!\N{\rEN}- I heard something go in the water! - Ambush! Ambush!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.48,1:34:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有东西掉进去了! - 跑 瑞米 跑!\N{\rEN}- Something went in! - Run. Remy. Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.15,1:34:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,慌乱中\N{\rEN}Panicking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.52,1:35:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达吓坏了 她开始跑\N{\rEN}Amanda got scared. She started running.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.42,1:35:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她就掉下去了 我是说 她就掉下去了\N{\rEN}She just fell. I mean, she just fell in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.80,1:35:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯·穆伦 29岁\N{\rEN}Twenty-nine-year-old Chris Mullen
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.03,1:35:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚被枪杀\N{\rEN}was gunned down last night
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.53,1:35:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原因显然是遭遇抢劫\N{\rEN}in an apparent robbery.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.87,1:35:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你进去陪陪弗兰 爸爸马上就进来\N{\rEN}You go back inside with Frannie. Papa will come in soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.07,1:35:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给你做三明治 好吗?\N{\rEN}Make you a sandwich, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.30,1:35:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 真是乖孩子\N{\rEN}- All right. - That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.61,1:35:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去那里\N{\rEN}Don't go down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.71,1:35:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我觉得他有证据 我来承担责任\N{\rEN}If I think he has the evidence, I'll take the hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.48,1:35:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有问题\N{\rEN}I got no problem doing the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.68,1:35:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 那是阿曼达和她的人生\N{\rEN}Fuck up, and it's Amanda and her life.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.18,1:35:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 我也有要保护的东西\N{\rEN}- All right. - I got things to protect, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.58,1:35:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是离开那间屋子 就是我的敌人\N{\rEN}You leave that house, you're an enemy to me
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.92,1:35:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你会伤害到阿曼达的\N{\rEN}and you're a danger to Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.18,1:35:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我告诉他为了勒索钱财绑架她 我已经说了\N{\rEN}Please, I told him we took her for ransom. I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.39,1:35:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他了 瑞米 求你了\N{\rEN}I told him. Remy, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.59,1:35:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了\N{\rEN}So now you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.73,1:35:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我妹妹生活不稳定 她嗑药\N{\rEN}My sister's not stable. She's on crack.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.30,1:35:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她说要离开这个州 我担心我的外甥女\N{\rEN}She's talking about leaving the state. I'm scared for my niece.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.47,1:35:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁来照顾她? - 我们要采取行动\N{\rEN}- Who's gonna take care of her? - We'll do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.74,1:35:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要想办法 她是瘾君子\N{\rEN}We'll figure it out. She's an addict.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.94,1:35:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,本性难移 无可救药\N{\rEN}Bigot. Drug mule.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.57,1:35:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子会死 或者不出10年就成为街上的太妹\N{\rEN}The child will be dead or on the street in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.71,1:35:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她舅舅怎么办? - 他不会告诉任何人\N{\rEN}- What about the uncle? - He can never tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.45,1:36:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,连他妻子都不告诉 否则他就再也见不到她\N{\rEN}Not even his wife. Or he'll never see her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.92,1:36:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说这值得 他知道她会过得更好\N{\rEN}It's worth it to him. Know she'll have a better life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.99,1:36:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们退休前 再做一件好事\N{\rEN}Do one last good thing before we hang it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.76,1:36:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们眼看着多少孩子被毁了?\N{\rEN}How many children have we seen destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.80,1:36:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,够多了\N{\rEN}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.90,1:36:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这样让你感觉好些吗?\N{\rEN}Does it make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.60,1:36:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你自己你做这件事 是出于正当的理由\N{\rEN}Telling yourself you did it for the right reasons?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.00,1:36:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了救她\N{\rEN}That you took her to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.41,1:36:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从母亲手里夺走她?\N{\rEN}From her own mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.44,1:36:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是要给 一个小女孩正常的人生\N{\rEN}We're just trying to give a little girl a life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.88,1:36:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能给她人生 海琳才是她妈妈\N{\rEN}Wasn't your life to give. Helene's her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.29,1:36:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得她不是合格的母亲 你应该找社会服务机构\N{\rEN}If you thought she was a bad mother, you should've gone to Social Services.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.09,1:36:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 她是她妈妈 那才是她的归宿\N{\rEN}Short of that, she's her mother, and that's where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.43,1:36:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你转身\N{\rEN}You turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.53,1:36:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,回到你的车上 等上30年\N{\rEN}You go back to your fucking car, and you wait 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.20,1:36:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不知道世界是怎么回事\N{\rEN}You don't know what the world is made of yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.97,1:37:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,5分钟后我会报警 他们10分钟后到\N{\rEN}I'm calling state police in five minutes. They'll be here in ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.14,1:37:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你本应该现在就做\N{\rEN}Thought you would've done that by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.25,1:37:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你为什么不那么做?\N{\rEN}You know why you haven't?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.39,1:37:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你想到这可能是个不可挽回的错误\N{\rEN}Because you think this might be an irreparable mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.39,1:37:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在你心灵深处 你知道法规怎么说都不重要\N{\rEN}Because deep inside you, you know it doesn't matter what the rules say.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.13,1:37:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当你熄灭灯光扪心自问\N{\rEN}When the lights go out and you ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.26,1:37:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"她在那更好还是在这更好?" 你知道答案\N{\rEN}"Is she better off here or better off there," you know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.23,1:37:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你会经常这样\N{\rEN}And you always will.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.10,1:37:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你有机会做正确的事\N{\rEN}You... You could do a right thing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.24,1:37:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一件善事\N{\rEN}A good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.15,1:37:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有人活一辈子都没有这样的机会\N{\rEN}Men live their whole lives without getting this chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.18,1:37:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你放弃机会\N{\rEN}You walk away from it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.15,1:37:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你回家的时候 不会觉得后悔\N{\rEN}you may not regret it when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.52,1:37:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能一整年都不后悔\N{\rEN}You may not regret it for a year,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.95,1:37:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当你处在我的位置 我保证 你会后悔\N{\rEN}but when you get to where I am, I promise you, you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.96,1:37:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我会离世 你会老去 但她…\N{\rEN}I'll be dead, you'll be old. But she...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.96,1:38:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她自己会拖着一群衣衫褴褛 脏乱不堪的孩子\N{\rEN}She'll be dragging around a couple of tattered, damaged children of her own,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.37,1:38:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你会是那个不得不跟她说对不起的人\N{\rEN}and you'll be the one who has to tell them you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.74,1:38:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗?那些事可能会发生\N{\rEN}You know what? Maybe that'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.01,1:38:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果发生了 我会道歉 我会承受一切\N{\rEN}And if it does, I'll tell them I'm sorry, and I'll live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.01,1:38:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有件事永远不会发生 我也不想做\N{\rEN}But what's never gonna happen and what I'm not gonna do
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.78,1:38:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是对一个长大了的女士道歉\N{\rEN}is have to apologize to a grown woman
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.59,1:38:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她过来对我说\N{\rEN}who comes to me and says,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.72,1:38:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候被绑架了\N{\rEN}"I was kidnapped when I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.89,1:38:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我舅妈雇了你来找我\N{\rEN}"and my aunt hired you to find me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.19,1:38:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了 你发现我在一个陌生的家庭\N{\rEN}"And you did, you found me with some strange family.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.83,1:38:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你违背了诺言 把我丢在那里\N{\rEN}"But you broke your promise and you left me there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.70,1:38:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?为什么你不带我回家?\N{\rEN}"Why? Why didn't you bring me home?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.84,1:38:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的零食 服装和旅游都不重要\N{\rEN}"Because all the snacks and the outfits and the family trips don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.24,1:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们偷偷带走了我\N{\rEN}"They stole me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.88,1:38:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的家庭 你知道的\N{\rEN}"It wasn't my family and you knew about it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.68,1:38:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你全都知道 但是无所作为\N{\rEN}"and you knew better and you did nothing."
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.62,1:38:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也许那个长大了的女士会原谅我\N{\rEN}And maybe that grown woman will forgive me,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.22,1:38:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我永远不会原谅我自己\N{\rEN}but I'll never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.86,1:39:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我做我该做的事 为了孩子\N{\rEN}I did what I did for the sake of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.23,1:39:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 也为了我\N{\rEN}All right. For me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.54,1:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在 我求你看在孩子的份上\N{\rEN}But now, I'm asking you for the sake of the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.51,1:39:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我恳求你\N{\rEN}I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.49,1:39:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑一下\N{\rEN}You think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.77,1:39:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她很开心\N{\rEN}She's happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.20,1:39:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.70,1:39:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这里很开心 我看到她了\N{\rEN}She's happy here. I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.11,1:39:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,安姬 不要这样\N{\rEN}Angie, don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.08,1:39:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你报警 她会被送回去\N{\rEN}If you call the police, they will send her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.18,1:39:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要把她送到别的地方去 海琳是她母亲\N{\rEN}I'm not sending her anywhere. Helene is her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.32,1:39:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这更好\N{\rEN}She's better off here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.95,1:40:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?因为他有钱 可以为她做三明治?\N{\rEN}Why? Because he's got money, and he makes her sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.12,1:40:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他爱她\N{\rEN}Because he loves her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.96,1:40:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 海琳也爱她 - 海琳不会那样善待她\N{\rEN}- Helene loves her, too. - Helene doesn't treat her that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.40,1:40:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 也许她会变\N{\rEN}Well, maybe she'll change.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.60,1:40:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会变 人们本性难移\N{\rEN}She won't change. People don't change.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.67,1:40:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳并非善类\N{\rEN}Helene is arsenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.34,1:40:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,安姬 我知道这很难\N{\rEN}Angie, I know that this is hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.64,1:40:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我 我知道很难\N{\rEN}Look at me, I know it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.04,1:40:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我需要你站在我这边 我要你说:\N{\rEN}But I need you to stand by me. I need you to say,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.41,1:40:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做了正确的决定\N{\rEN}"We're gonna make the right decision,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.61,1:40:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会让事情好转\N{\rEN}"and we're gonna make everything okay."
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.91,1:40:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好的\N{\rEN}Everything will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.12,1:40:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们要把她留在这\N{\rEN}Because we're gonna leave her here,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.32,1:40:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会不时谈起她\N{\rEN}and every now and then we're gonna talk about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.55,1:40:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪里 她读几年级\N{\rEN}And where she is, and about what grade she's in.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.32,1:40:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好 因为我们知道 她在什么学校里\N{\rEN}And that'll be okay, because we're gonna know what school she's in,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.86,1:40:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会知道她很快乐 她有生日聚会\N{\rEN}and we're gonna know she's happy, and she's got birthday parties,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.30,1:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每天她都欢笑 一觉睡到天亮\N{\rEN}and she smiles every day, and she has sleepovers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.57,1:40:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 对不起\N{\rEN}Baby, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.64,1:40:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能要我做一些我做不到的事情\N{\rEN}But you can't ask me to do something that I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.44,1:40:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你也不能要我忍受这样的事\N{\rEN}And you can't ask me to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.78,1:41:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,帕特里克 为了我 求你了?\N{\rEN}Patrick, for me. Please?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.49,1:41:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会因此恨你 而我不想这样\N{\rEN}I will hate you for doing this, and I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.38,1:42:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经是正义的象征 勇士的楷模\N{\rEN}Once an icon of justice and a model for crusaders,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.22,1:42:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·道伊尔今晚锒铛入狱 埃芙琳?\N{\rEN}Jack Doyle is behind bars tonight. Evelyn?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.92,1:42:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,根据法律要求 社会服务机构\N{\rEN}Social Services, as demanded by law,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.12,1:42:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会先花些时间对阿曼达体检 然后再带她回家\N{\rEN}will take time to examine little Amanda before returning her to home,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.53,1:42:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,回到母亲的怀抱\N{\rEN}and the arms of a mother who never gave up hope
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.66,1:42:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这位母亲从未放弃再次看到女儿的希望\N{\rEN}that she would see her daughter again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.27,1:43:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 海琳 你觉得怎么样… - 海琳 感觉如何\N{\rEN}- Helene, how do you feel... - Helene, what does it feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.11,1:43:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在你和女儿团聚了? - 觉得怎么样?\N{\rEN}- to have your daughter with you now? - How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.04,1:43:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳 你现在觉得好吗?感觉怎么样…\N{\rEN}Helene, how you feeling right now? How you feeling...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.85,1:43:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,后退 后退 后退\N{\rEN}Back up. Back up. Back up. Back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.62,1:43:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼达 看到妈妈感觉怎么样?\N{\rEN}Amanda, how do you feel to see your mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.98,1:43:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 阿曼达\N{\rEN}Hey, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.75,1:43:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,海琳 你觉得怎样?\N{\rEN}Helene, how you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.86,1:43:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉我们你的感觉 - 告诉我们你现在在想什么\N{\rEN}- Tell us how it feels. - Tell us what you're thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.86,1:43:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很激动 告诉我们你的感受\N{\rEN}You must be so excited. Give us your feelings.
